d good 1hd and start using my shield more or should I stick with the 2hder?<br><br>I know that 1 factor is where I'm tanking or not and the group make up is important but I'm just looking for a generalization of what makes more sense?  I'm seeing a lot of Paladins on Tunare use the new AC25 Wis+20 from Lulcin along with a 1hder rather then a bigger damage 2hd.  <br><br>I also have a haste belt 32%.  Personally I think the 2hder is the way to go but I want to see what some of my fellow paladins say.<br><br> <p>Deffcon DeathBane <br>51 Level Paladin <br>Deffender of Marr <br><img src=http://eqvault.ign.com/features/artwork/ghoulsbane_thumb.jpg> <br><a href=http://www.ezboard.com>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=42584</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uangelsyn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Angelsyn</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://members.aol.com/tdlutenatenjou/icon_keyne.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 160<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(3/13/02 1:01:29 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=197.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/tdlutenatenjou/icon_keyne.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: 1hd vs. 2hd, hmmmmm.</span><hr size=1> Your profile needs updating... you're not showing a Haste Belt.<br><br>If you're going to PoA anyway, try convincing your Guild to farm Island 4 so you can get your Quest Haste Belt.<br><br>For damage, 2h beats 1h every time in the high end.<br><br>Your Sta is low (it's only 110 because of the shield.)  I recomend a Crusty Bracer to replace that Hero Bracer.<br><br>Also, Head to Maidens and get one of the Idols that drop there. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=2